Jean-Louis Weissberg. « La crise fiduciaire des medias de masse. Je crois parce que j’experimente. »  Multitudes 21, http://www.multitudes.net/La-crise-fiduciaire-des-medias-de/

I particularly recommend the above essay, an extended meditation on the crisis of trust affecting institutional media, and the epistemological characteristics of the new situation.

It's part of a special issue of the French journal Multitudes on the topic of subjectivation in the postmedia age

